== Alexander Van der Bellen == ryax sa tay 18 nqo tay 1, Alexander Van der Bellen, sqoliq na sezi'. (minhtow sa kawas tay 1944) mrhow Aostria ta' misow hya' ga Alexander Van der Bellen, aring ryax tay 26 sqo byacing tay 1 sa kawas 2017 lga, mosa' spazyang balay ms'rox kya la. qnxan nya Alexander Van der Bellen maki tay kawas 1962 msqon ki Sandra Davenport, maki tay kawas 2015 t'alax. pinqbaqan nya Alexander Van der Bellen, kawas tay 1966 malax mqwas biro sa Innsbrock pqwsan biro kraho . mintzyowaw nya Alexander Van der Bellen sa kawas 1994, t'aring mtzyowaw zyowaw na sezi. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro'
